==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æstɪk|-æstɪk]]

===Adjective===
'''nastic'''

# Relates to the movement of a [[plant]] in response to a [[stimulus]], regardless of its direction, such as the opening of a flower in response to light or temperature, or the wilting of [[mimosa]] on being touched.

